quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,38,"[Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen] wi'a : \"Naate e moftaaji, gom…óii yawtii ado mon immorde e jinna e yim…ďe ka nder Yiite\". Tuma kala nde mofte naati, …óe hu…óa banndam majje. Haa si …ďe tawtindirii ton …ďe denndaanal, sakkitii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen wi'ana aram…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen : \"Joomi amen! Ko …ďee majjini men : Okku …ďe lepte cowan…óe e Yiite ngen\". O Daala : \"Hino woodani kala [mon] cowan…óe, kono on anndaa"
  7,39,"Aram…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen wi'ana sakkitii…ďe …ďen : \"Alanaa on e dow amen …ďural, mee…óiree lepte …óen sabu kon ko faggitotono…óon"
  7,40,"Pellet, …ďen fennu…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe townitanii …óe, …ďe udditantaake dame kammuuli …óin, …ďe naatataa kadi Aljanna haa ngelooba naata e wuddere meselal. Ko wano non Men yo…ďirte …ďom…ďe …ďen"
  7,41,"Hino woodani …ďe ka Jahannama nda…ó…óudi, no dow ma…ď…ďe kadi kippoodi. Ko wanon non Men yo…ďirta too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  7,42,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói - Men fawataa wonkii si wanaa ko ki waawi - Ko …ďen …óon woni yim…ďe Aljanna : kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton"
  7,43,"Men …ďoori e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen konnaagu, can…ói …óin no ila senngo ley ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'a : \"Yettoore woodani Alla On fewu…óo men e …óum …óoo, men wonaano feewoo…ďe si Alla fewnaano men. Gom…óii Nulaa…ďe Joomi amen …ďen addii goonga\". ∆Āe noddee si ko woni : \"On …óon moo…óon Aljanna, on roninaama mo, sabu kon ko gollayno…óon"
